---
title: Open-Faced Mushroom Melts with Tomato-Onion Jam
description: Crisp ciabatta rolls topped with hearty mushrooms and a savoury tomato-onion jam are a match made in sandwich heaven. The melted mozzarella is the bonus you never knew you wanted, but absolutely need!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-ouverts-aux-champignons-fromages-ab40f15d.jpg
